      "description": "# 0.1.0\n\n## Added\n\n- Initial FloatMark release with Feishu-style floating selection toolbar\n- Left-side block hover menu for formatting, comments, copy, and delete\n- Inline highlight marks in edit and reading mode with configurable colors\n- Sidebar comment threads with edit, reply, resolve, and jump-to-source\n- Optional Feishu / Lark comment sync\n- Local sidecar storage under `.obsidian-float-marks/`\n- Anchor relocation after small text edits\n\n## Improved\n\n- Bilingual README documentation\n- Lark sync settings and sidebar UI polish\n",
